sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller as 调用方
    participant Proxy as 代理对象
    participant RMI as ReflectiveMethodInvocation
    participant Adv1 as @Before Advice
    participant Adv2 as @Around Advice
    participant Target as 目标方法
    participant Adv3 as @After Advice
    participant Adv4 as @AfterReturning Advice

    Caller->>Proxy: method()
    Proxy->>RMI: proceed()
    RMI->>Adv1: before()
    Adv1-->>RMI: 继续
    RMI->>Adv2: around(proceed)
    Adv2->>Target: invoke()
    Target-->>Adv2: result
    Adv2->>Adv3: after()
    Adv3-->>Adv2: 继续
    Adv2->>Adv4: afterReturning(result)
    Adv4-->>Adv2: 继续
    Adv2-->>RMI: result
    RMI-->>Proxy: result
    Proxy-->>Caller: result

    Note over Adv1,Adv4: Advice 链按 Advisor 顺序递归执行<br/>任意 Advice 抛异常会跳过后续 Advice<br/>进入 @AfterThrowing 链
